text: Josip Ćuk (19 March 1936 - 25 April 2019) was a Yugoslav sports shooter. He competed in the 300 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Yugoslav male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Yugoslavia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Donja Stubica
